-- BofA to Delay Process to Amend Affidavits in Foreclosure Cases
-- B y   H e a t h e r   B u r k e
-- 2010-10-01T20:56:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-01/bofa-to-delay-process-to-amend-affidavits-in-foreclosure-cases.html
Bank of America Corp. said it will
delay the foreclosure process in order to amend all affidavits
in cases that have not yet gone to judgment in the 23 states
where courts have jurisdiction over foreclosures. The
information was released in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Heather Burke at 
 hburke2@bloomberg.net  